TableBooking (Tabook)

Eliza Nie (yn9sa)
Qian Xiong (qx2dk)

User Stories
1. As a user, I want to sign up on the website.
2. As a user, I want to sign in the website.
3. As a customer, I want to search for a particular restaurant by name on the website.
4. As a customer, I want to see a list of nearby restaurants.
5. As a customer, I want to sort restaurants by a certain criteria (popularity/ numbers of reviews/ distance/etc)
6. As a customer, I want to search for an available table by the number of people and by the meal time.
7. As a customer, I want to view the restaurant menu.
8. As a customer, I want to reserve a table.
9. As a customer, I want to cancel a reservation.
10. As a customer, I want to receive an email/text reminder before the reserved time.
11. As a restaurant, I want to create and update my restaurant profile/menu.
12. As a user, I want to the reservation status to be up-to-date.
13. As a restaurant, I want to be able to manually update available tables.
14. As a restaurant, I want to receive a notification for any reservation.
